.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_info -  This method sets information about the deity.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_info(string deity,
string text)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^deity%^RESET%^ - the name of the deity to set information for
%^BOLD%^text%^RESET%^ - the new value for the information

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/deity_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets information about the deity.  This is used
in the finger information and when querying about joining the
clergy.
.EP

